Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:05.49,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是手包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:08.08,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你到底打算干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:10.16,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是说过要抛手包吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:12.54,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}刚才还漂亮地抛起了三个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:18.84,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不相信我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:20.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:22.51,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的很漂亮地抛起了三个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:23.22,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}晚安…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:24.47,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:26.05,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你快回去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:27.68,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我还在放哨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:31.06,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}主人要给你看拿手绝活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:35.23,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}做臣子的不是该跪下恭恭敬敬地拜见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:36.40,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别胡搅蛮缠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:38.48,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  我命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:39.98,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  等等！ 等等！ 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:44.74,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别在这种时候用主人的命令来压我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:47.78,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我可不想再立什么多余的誓言了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:52.41,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}疼疼疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:54.33,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别咬人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:57.54,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还不怪你自己太粗暴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:02.97,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:05.97,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我看着就是了  你快点抛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.35,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你说的话… 总是这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:09.89,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:10.47,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:13.85,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想看想得不得了  你快点抛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.48,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还是那么一点诚意也没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:18.36,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:21.57,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看过我的绝技之后  你的态度也就会变了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:26.74,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我终于找到窍门了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:30.49,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哼  学会了之后就是这么简单的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:33.91,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}现在  我已经是不输给里叶的手包名人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:40.80,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我终于明白  全心全意去学习一件事物是多么地重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:42.55,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:58.31,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}刚才那绝对是搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.79,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我没说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:19.92,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的已经学会了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.59,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}谁也没说你说谎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.30,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我看着呢  你尽管抛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:27.93,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.43,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}肩膀放松一些嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.39,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不放松一些的话  名人也做不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:33.85,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是… 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:39.56,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.27,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么样  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:44.65,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我抛得不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.95,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}能做到这样已经很了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.95,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}用不着安慰我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:54.33,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这不是安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:57.87,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}能做成这样  是因为你努力练习了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:05:00.54,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不懂得放弃可真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:04.09,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}听不懂你到底是在夸我还是在嘲笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.51,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是在夸你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.80,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不管怎么说  你干得很好  神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.09,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我还想做得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:13.97,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}每天都练习的话肯定会变得很拿手的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:15.60,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:16.97,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:21.56,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你还会再看我抛手包吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:24.61,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  只要你愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:28.07,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}趁现在快去睡一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:29.24,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天还要走很多路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:30.24,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:48.13,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看来必须越过这些群山峻岭才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:54.30,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想逃脱追兵的话  在山林里行进是再好不过的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:56.56,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我去取些水来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:05.61,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么了  神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:13.57,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:20.16,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}求你饶了我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:23.87,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}进不去了… 都说过进不去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:26.09,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}饶了我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.42,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:33.51,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已经吃不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.76,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  这么睡的话会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.49,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  别再睡第二觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.41,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也别睡第三觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:03.00,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人  您太手软了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.22,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很疼的啊  你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:19.60,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人  您感觉好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:22.31,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你看我像感觉好的样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:25.14,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}叫我起床时就不能再温柔些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:28.86,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那么下次我就再注意一下力度…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:31.94,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是让你别再抽枕头了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:43.41,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的耳朵可真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.67,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}跑起来的话不会刮到草木上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:51.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}耳朵这么长的话  可以听得很远吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:00.35,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可恶  居然敢耍我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:01.64,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  给我停下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:03.56,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}给我停下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.56,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂！ 停下停下停下停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:07.06,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:08.60,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}给我安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:13.48,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你一直在看什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:15.70,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}前几天在集市上找到的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.28,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很珍贵的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:20.99,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这些像虫子一样的东西是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:21.95,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是河流的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.70,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈  你不认识字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:26.91,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没有人教我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:28.87,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又怎么可能认识呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.79,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}里叶居然也不管你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:32.80,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我才没有不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:38.47,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为神奈大人说过「绝对不想跟里叶学字」…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.68,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那不是要怪里叶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:43.26,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}该不会忘了歌集那件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:46.98,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是为了丰富神奈大人的心灵才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:49.69,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}靠你那种教人的方法  心灵怎么会丰富得起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:51.06,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你们在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:56.19,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}以前  我曾经教过神奈大人背诵和歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:59.49,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}学习东西当然要付出一点点心血了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:02.07,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是神奈大人却…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:06.66,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一天要背二百首  还叫什么「一点点心血」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:09.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一共有四千五百首呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.96,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}磨磨蹭蹭怎么行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.80,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已经五天没睡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:20.01,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还剩下二百首  再忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:23.30,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的命还真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:24.89,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:27.43,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想这样下去肯定会死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:30.56,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以把歌集全都扔到炉灶里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:35.23,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}宝贵的古今六帖一并全都变成早饭的柴火了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:40.07,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那天的饭  真是充满了风流的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:44.70,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是这张嘴在胡说八道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:46.62,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快放开… 里叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:50.33,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}连一首和歌也唱不出来的嘴巴  根本就是没用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:52.04,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}太没道理了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:54.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我干脆把它缝上算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.09,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你还在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.42,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:01.84,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  我也怕里叶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:04.47,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你这没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:10.60,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对不起  我有些太激动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.44,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.27,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么你要原谅她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:15.69,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的声音还是很怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.78,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:20.86,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我到那边去练习抛手包了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:23.20,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在这里待着心会乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:26.08,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那我也陪你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:27.87,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}用不着你陪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:34.33,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么要打我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.92,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我在乱发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:44.01,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:03.28,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是和尚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:04.95,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}身上没有伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.74,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看来是累倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.26,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:25.97,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}能说一会话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.14,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.18,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又要抛手包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:30.01,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:34.35,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是不是有什么心事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:36.56,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}心事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:37.44,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:41.65,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有什么想说的话不必憋在心里  把它说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.15,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.37,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那我就说一句好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:49.58,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:51.91,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的头顶上有只毛毛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:59.79,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你好像很容易吸引野兽和虫子之类的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:02.42,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别那么冷静啊  就不能救救我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:06.26,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}刚才就一直觉得你很古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:09.09,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}本来想作为主人关心一下臣子来着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.85,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}结果弄得自己这么没面子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:14.35,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉  我说给你听就是了  别走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:17.69,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不会再拿我开玩笑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:20.94,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这可是很无聊的事情哦  你真的想听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:22.61,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你尽管说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:27.40,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我没见过自己的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:29.37,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:32.12,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}大概  是被扔掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:35.58,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在路边哭泣的时候  被行脚僧捡到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:38.79,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}行脚僧就是旅行的和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:43.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所谓的行脚僧听起来似乎很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:47.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其实也只是无家可归  四处乞讨的人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:51.85,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我们俩一起周游了各种各样的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:56.02,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}北方 南方 东方 西方  去过各种各样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:00.35,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他是柳也的养育之亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:02.65,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也算不上是什么养育之亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:07.99,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他是个严厉的人  除了诵经之外从不开口说闲话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:11.37,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就连法名最终也没有告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:15.83,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在大约五岁时的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.42,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我们在山路上遇到了山贼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:25.75,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}行脚僧被一刀杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:29.13,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看到刚才那个和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:31.26,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想起了这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:35.85,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}原来柳也也没有母亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:41.90,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  我却只顾追寻自己的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:43.61,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:45.77,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这也是我的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:51.78,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个行脚僧临死前还在祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:55.53,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}祝愿杀死自己的人能够往升净土
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:59.83,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}之后  自己死在了血泊中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:02.29,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我没有被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:06.55,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他们说我不值得弄脏他们的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:10.76,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就这样  我又独自一人站在路边了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:18.56,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那以后  我一直都是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:21.69,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为了活下去  我什么都干过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.73,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}偷走过别人的刀枪  参加过战争
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:26.52,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也杀过人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:29.86,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}每天都只想着自己如何才能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:33.74,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}直到最近为止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:34.70,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最近…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:35.82,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最近发生过什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:40.54,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这就是所谓的心境转变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:43.83,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要有一些契机  人都会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:48.67,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那些山贼一定也很后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:52.55,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他们杀了一位德高望重的高僧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.22,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}当然会后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:58.10,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很难说他能不能算得上是德高望重的高僧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:00.22,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在怀疑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:03.10,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}正是因为听到了行脚僧的祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:06.77,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}山贼们才没有杀害柳也吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:14.57,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:19.45,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个时候  我或许确实是被行脚僧救了一条命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:22.96,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么没有早点注意到这一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:25.87,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那样的话  我就一定会走上另一条道路了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:27.42,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:30.96,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那样的话  我不是就遇不到柳也了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.26,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:35.38,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也庆幸自己能遇到神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:38.68,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:43.39,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:45.98,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:47.60,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:48.44,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:52.23,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不知道接下来该怎么做才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:55.82,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:59.07,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}后边的事就拜托给柳也了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:11.04,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我很难为情的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:12.25,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:13.71,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:17.26,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你真的知道接下来要干什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:19.60,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别… 别小看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:21.10,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我很清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:23.31,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}里叶全都教给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.89,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}果然是里叶捣的鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:27.44,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:29.81,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也对我来说就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.65,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然说不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:34.15,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但是… 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:38.61,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}里叶说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:43.87,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「柳也说起往事的时候  就别放过那个机会」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:49.67,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}男性是一定会对喜欢的女性说起往事来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.88,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:54.42,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}都被她猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:58.93,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「听柳也说完后  就慢慢地解开衣服」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:03.68,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她还说过什么「需要让胸部若隐若现」之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:06.31,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}连导演都做好了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:09.19,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我弄错什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:14.57,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}莫非  柳也只喜欢男色吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:15.82,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:17.28,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:20.66,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有些男性虽然喜欢女性  却很无能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.12,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别胡说八道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:26.45,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}果然还是因为把衣服脱得过头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.12,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:33.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就让你知道我也是个男人  你做好准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:36.46,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也  你的眼神很怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.59,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是你来引诱我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:40.63,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就老老实实让我用毒牙咬一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:43.30,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳… 柳也有毒的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:45.22,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}男人全都是有毒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:48.60,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而且还有更多你不知道的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:53.11,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就让我一步一步教你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.77,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  快住手！ 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:58.03,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:02.28,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}里叶  你藏在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:03.03,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:07.87,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你依然是那么精明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.50,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人  您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:19.76,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不太清楚… 不过似乎不太成功…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:21.43,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:25.85,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我惹柳也生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:28.22,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我没生气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.15,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}里叶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:36.36,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是不是看穿我绝对不会出手的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.82,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其实我自己也不是很确定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.23,0:18:41.82,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}天下哪还有我这种人畜无害的男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:44.16,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也可以说是无能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:45.37,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}罗嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.42,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她睡得很香嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:59.09,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天也热心地做过手包的修炼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:03.63,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}睡着的时候  倒是很可爱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:05.89,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在无聊男人们聚过来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:08.56,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}得教会她色恋之事才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:10.22,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别用我来练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:12.64,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:16.52,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}连人偶和手包都没有玩过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:20.28,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}母亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:23.36,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}您醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:27.74,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我做了一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:31.24,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是一个在其他地方的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:35.62,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我穿着奇特的衣装  相貌也改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:39.38,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那真的是我吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.09,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}变成什么样的相貌了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:44.34,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}记不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:47.01,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过  身边有我的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.81,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还有很多善良的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:53.10,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我非常地幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:56.65,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是个很好的梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:59.82,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要把这个梦变成现实不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.27,0:20:02.32,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你马上就能见到母亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:05.61,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那时候  你的梦就不再是梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:07.07,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:11.45,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要虔诚祈祷  上天就一定能够听到我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:24.97,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看啊  看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:26.51,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我做得很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:28.30,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}它们没有掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.30,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一个也没有掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.15,0:20:49.57,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看来还需要再修炼一段时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:53.29,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过  真的是很棒啊  神奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:57.71,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要继续修炼下去  一定会更加出色的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.12,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:02.71,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到时候我就可以做给母亲看了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:04.25,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:17.10,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我们该走了  神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:21.69,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么了  不和我一起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:35.29,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是你的母亲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:37.83,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:48.34,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要永远幸福地生活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:05.90,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:07.61,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}何だ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:13.20,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也殿に　お願いがあるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:19.29,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}まだ　ちと恥ずかしいが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:20.50,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}見てくれるか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:54.98,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}ではゆくぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:58.48,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}ちょっと待てぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:02.99,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}それは何だ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:04.41,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}見てわからぬのか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:05.49,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}お手玉だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:08.08,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}お前はこれから何をするつもりだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:10.16,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}だからお手玉だと申しておろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:12.54,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}先きちんと三つ舞ったのだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:18.84,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}その目は疑っておるな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:20.17,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}まことだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:22.51,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}まことに三つ綺麗に舞わせたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:23.22,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}お休み…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:24.47,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}寝るでない！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:26.05,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}寝所に戻れ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:27.68,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}こっちは見張り中なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:31.06,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}主は修練の技を見せてやると申しておるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:35.23,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}ひれ伏して拝見するのが臣下の務めというものであろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:36.40,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}無茶苦茶言うな！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:38.48,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}では　余はお主に命ずるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:39.98,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}あぁ！　待って待って待って！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:44.74,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}こんな時に主従の命なんかを持ち出すのは反則だろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:47.78,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}これ以上余計な誓いを増やされてはたまるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:52.41,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}痛って　てぇてぇてぇ　たたたたた！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:54.33,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一々噛むな！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:57.54,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}お主は手荒な真似をするからだろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:02.97,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}わかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:05.97,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}見てやるから　早めにさっさと済ませてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.35,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}お主の　そういう物言い方が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:09.89,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}わかった　わかった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:10.47,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}見たい！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:13.85,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}ぜひ拝見しとうございますから早くやってくれぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.48,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}相変わらず誠意のない言葉だの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:18.36,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}まあ良いわ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:21.57,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}余の手さばきを見ればその態度も変わるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:26.74,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}余はついにコツを掴んだのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:30.49,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}出来るようになってみれば造作もないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:33.91,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今や裏葉にも負けぬほどのお手玉の名人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:40.80,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}心を尽くして何かに習い務めることの大切さを今こそわかった気がするぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:42.55,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}見よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:58.31,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今のは何かの間違いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.79,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘘ではないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:19.92,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}本当にちゃんとできたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.59,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}だれも嘘だなんて言ってないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.30,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}見ててやるから　何度でもやってみろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:27.93,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今度こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.43,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}肩の力を抜けよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.39,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}落ち着いてやらないと名人でもうまくできないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:33.85,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}そ　そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:39.56,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}参るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.27,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}どうだ どうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:44.65,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}できたであろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.95,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}これだけできれば大したもんさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.95,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}慰めなどいらぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:54.33,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}慰めじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:57.87,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}そこまでできるようになったのは　お前ががんばったからだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:05:00.54,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}あきらめが悪いってのはすごいことだな
