Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:29.24,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今日も歩き詰めだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:30.24,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}うん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:48.13,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}この山々を越えないといけないわけか
