Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:05.61,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}どうした　神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:13.57,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}痛てぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:20.16,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}許して… たもれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:23.87,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}入らぬ　入らぬと言うに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:26.09,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}許して
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.42,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}これ以上は…　もう…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:33.51,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}もう食べられぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.76,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}おい！　そんな格好で寝てたら風邪引くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.49,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}おい　二度寝するな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.41,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}三度寝もするな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:03.00,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也様　手ぬるいですわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.22,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}痛いぞ　何をするか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:19.60,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈様にあらせられましては　ご機嫌麗しゅう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:22.31,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}これは麗しい機嫌に見えるか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:25.14,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}もう少し優しく起こせぬのか
