Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.09,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}にゃにほひてほるー
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.42,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}ひゃほふにはすへんは～
